source.description: This GTFS data for Rift Valley Railways Kenya has been developed by the Nairobi Mobility Team through a collaboration between University of Nairobi School of Computing & Informatics, Columbia University CSUD, MIT Civic Data Design Lab and Groupshot, and has been supported by The Rockefeller Foundation.
